text: I don't know how you are feeling right now. It's true there's someone in your heart.
Won't you please let me know. She belongs to you, cos your smile isn't there anymore.
All these years I've try to let you know that love. I want you, I need you. But, I couldn't say it to you.
Thus I cried inside. Please believe me. I do regret from the start.
I know it's too late to cry now, too late to cry now. It's too late to turn back now.
Only hope you'll change your mind. I know it's too late to cry now, too late to cry now.
It's too late to turn back now. I know my love.
